{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170060/extras/new_demo_banner.png?t=1728948884\" />We've recently updated our demo \u2014 the first third of the game is now available for free! Once you're done, you can continue where you left off in the full game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170060/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1728948884\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170060/extras/steam-page-throw-yourself.gif?t=1728948884\" />Carving through hordes of horrors isn\u2019t the only thing your boomerang is good for: once thrown, you can slingshot directly to it, preserving momentum and launching yourself through the air. Slow down time and use well-aimed throws to get around, above, and behind your foes. Speed is everything, and only the nimblest boomerang-er will survive\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170060/extras/steam-page-powers.gif?t=1728948884\" />Fight otherworldly forces and look cool doing it. Impress the boomerang with stylish tricks and it\u2019ll grant you strange powers to let you defeat the forces of the depths with greater ease. Kaspidae smiles upon you and your killer moves\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170060/extras/steam-page-monsters.gif?t=1728948884\" />They creep and crawl from crevices, swoop and dive from the treetops, and spray nasty bile at you from all angles. Keep your wits about you \u2014 nowhere is safe. Whatever you do, don\u2019t stand still, or you\u2019ll surely be consumed...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170060/extras/steam-page-realm.gif?t=1728948884\" />Fight your way through the bowels of a ruined civilization and stop the nightmares from spreading to the rest of your world. Something lurks deep underneath these ruined halls, spewing corruption\u2026 can you defeat whatever it is? And even if you can\u2026 will that really be the end?</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Boomerang X","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/ecf0e1e5404676ce5aa4b3044448405f0d67a41d.jpg"},{"name":"Composer\u2019s Garden","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/1150e3e8568b9b46df342ad6a9f9b9926892553a.jpg"},{"name":"Kenak, the Exiled Tyrant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/e05cc4d5e98f425d56b1e4d83aba5b92784f1d49.jpg"},{"name":"The Grudge Pit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/f6029655b293b3103ee9ed63cca5174156986a65.jpg"},{"name":"The Valley of the First Nymphs","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/292b025cdbf608eacf390b4abfe7a0f46910c7f5.jpg"},{"name":"Yoranwood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/fd77c18e87cb01214c8645640c63b2702cbdbbb1.jpg"},{"name":"The Poisoned Well","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/8b51958e272ad04da465c895693d84be3ca7ef8b.jpg"},{"name":"Incursion of the Great Worm","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1170060/4379f9fb213776d1133c4c43950e309a33687ad7.jpg"},{"name":"The Old Vein","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap